Subject: drm/amd/display: Add W/A for PHY tests with certain LTTPR
Git-commit: 81bb9bc95355055e2fa297b9a81e9d786eca9903
Patch-mainline: v5.17-rc1
References: jsc#PED-1166 jsc#PED-1168 jsc#PED-1170 jsc#PED-1218 jsc#PED-1220 jsc#PED-1222 jsc#PED-1223 jsc#PED-1225

[Why]
Certain LTTPR require output VS/PE to be explicitly
set during PHY test automation.

[How]
Add vendor-specific sequence to set LTTPR
output VS/PE.

